      "content": "i see, so basically u mean that even if there's a local tradition, it's better to stick to the western way to look professional? like if someone is wearing traditional clothing or using their hands to eat in a business setting, u're saying that's less \"sophisticated\" than using silverwear and a suit? why is that the standard for competence though?",
